# Plesk / Phusion Passenger entry point.
#
# In Plesk, use:
# - Application root: project root
# - Document root: project-root/public
# - Startup file: server.js
# - Application mode: production
#
# Some Plesk installations read Passenger settings from the panel UI instead
# of .htaccess. Keep this file in public so the document root has a clear entry
# point and deployment note.
PassengerEnabled on
PassengerAppEnv production
